[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating log4j thresholds**\n\nI’m thinking about how the test level threshold should meet the criteria for assigning priorities. I wonder if the need level can extend the priority settings, but maybe that’s not necessary? I should dig into the specifics of log4j 2.18 and see how the levels are defined. It seems like there are some nuances here that I need to clarify to ensure everything aligns properly with the existing structure.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_08a982de9bcae927016a3e91dd028c819797cc1b3d68572a08\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqPpHfxdIfybXaGcT0Z2crYZlO5sC1hu6OgR1eaGL9xgSMua0TmT5qMgPXsMeBiSpkzCxcP3RWARA0w5UCt1pR7X_iEtV7LcTmoOFHKTA4kfG7QENEcZgKJS2rVoCE9cMtdA_ibqt6b_D51MNNeUjr6HpjnhMqyy94MPpPemYU6vfIl9-wkKOOuMbMyd7AgE8GKuiGLbfVWZvje2BXHnSRvLrwQbZMdofEI03uLVzto9d2fqzrJnidnWIPL6fIUmi-8ShTIMG8KWM4CUbtFI9BpnT30vLHzk_xbi-pI6Q3U47Hue12-eNeWAHv89S4vq8p2pehXv3mazlDChisdfelsjQE_5gAJUh5-GiSAJRy7_hOGBr00ndPbDeImxI3u7w9vLts-EjbB-u41O21VLAwfK8IOKYAHIhGPJ98Ca6FCmLT4u2_yZyTRv3YPNetGio6iW2A3-ls4w3ErZiAD9C7INfnMgOrCPN9uAynBiZbz3skc5sB7VuI3FjiwHc2J1fR0M4gjhWkNsWaLqHgl2bpBclb6d3gA0u50TMUCv54LGWf1v5lAonXeVFLIXHlQONgMFDqj2VQikzBT0wSlUh2vYRJGEnGURZr0sg7h7t0GrXkWHIof-wLaWpMv1aSt5MpA6roYaKHjXJV5U7S8aQ6R54WeVt2yHXcOHDU6SPZFKoSv4PJN0phHYnupkpK50OJbNFSEkyuEBVMe_CJkUHJjEPm4YKsnyGhycA-Q19NcpB3C2LGtNtC8diY3ZIKQOwBo5KUx9LaGRqt01kv9CPW0F84Uz0VHawy-FSYFkOz5uobKHUmLaTsKhP78kwasS-kHSoPpGYEQMXrdwj8RBqX_Xy3UgCqhv6Vy8UlsfHnkjfg9kaGWY-QvIzxCHp4DIux5JWUXOuCYqSuHzyWtOuxM0O_ag4dXTXjyw0TEqLhUbyjllOFHXuw3Pe3Y9zu4rrPzhZho9-3NKpKLmNkvL9HVhPiNCdjYSMSQvJN7lJ6o3NQLxH5z_htko8GCV-vOudVtGNJJ2omr_Y_tmZP6i4bMbV94w0ea0gXHSOYqoGCxMIlfbVZD3DMFymOlPEYQy-b9i4UUcb3nus83vDI4Tedbi5d0A==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating log4j thresholds**\\n\\nI’m thinking about how the test level threshold should meet the criteria for assigning